ina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the strict regime\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"a major role\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"their success\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even with our best performance, we would have finished sixth today,' Barthel said.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our best performance\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And in Germany, a medal counts.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9905393158975634, \"rank\": 0.008640101182466586, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone talks and reports about it.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone talks\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"reports\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And whether we finish fourth or seventh does not make much difference.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much difference\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am proud of us and happy that we made it and qualified.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were in the final, we are in seventh place, and no one can take that away from us.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"seventh place\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was the toughest competition this year.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the toughest competition\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Insane.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Insane\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know if I have ever seen a 490 before.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Awesome competition.'\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Awesome competition\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking about the sacrifices made by China's divers ahead of the Olympics in Paris, Barthel said: 'They live in a boarding school, four to a room.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8121564267532068, \"rank\": 0.15595426142310126, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999997749, \"rank\": 2.2579972636372093e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sacrifices\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"a boarding school\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"a room\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They train for twelve hours.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"twelve hours\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not know anything other than diving.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not have a private life like we do where we go out with a girlfriend or partner, eat ice cream, go to restaurants, meet family.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a private life\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"a girlfriend\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"partner\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"ice cream\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes they do not see their family for three years.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their family\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That is the difference between absolute world class and our performance today.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"absolute world class\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"our performance\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the question is also - do \\u200b\\u200byou want it that way?\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u200b\\u200byou\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you want to have a life like that so that you can have gold?'\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barthel also admits that the prize money on offer for winning gold is not enough to convince him to adopt the lifestyle of China's athletes.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}, {\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8121564267532068, \"rank\": 0.15595426142310126, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prize money\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"offer\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"the lifestyle\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I heard on the news that we get \\u20ac20,000 [\\u00a316,800] for a gold medal in Germany.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9905393158975634, \"rank\": 0.008640101182466586, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is it worth it?\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For \\u20ac20,000?\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That you put your whole life on hold?'\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your whole life\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barthel said.\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We already do that.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not live in Aachen anymore.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9998329294294854, \"rank\": 0.00016652869204387348, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbped